# iOS PWA UX

- Account for iOS PWA behavior in mobile UI work.
- Check safe-area insets, dynamic viewport height, `visualViewport`, keyboard behavior, bottom nav overlap, scroll restore, and horizontal overflow.
- Avoid fixed or sticky layout changes without considering iOS Safari and PWA mode.
- Be extra careful with chat composer, feed scroll, modals, sheets, and mobile tab bar.
- Keep mobile UI compact and Russian-language.
